@node Main "Tri_it - Documentation"

                                 Tri_it 1.02

                         Created by Charles-N. Jacob

  "Tri_it" is a Workbench game where you try to match the
triangular shaped pattern shown on the left in the least amount
of moves possible.

  There are 4 sizes of game boards you can @{" choose " link play} and except for
the smallest board (which I call the 'practice board') the game
counts the number of moves you make.

  Have fun!

  @{" Features     " link features}      What are its features?
